comments: Williams (MIL) makes marginal contact to Musa's (BKN) back with a resting forearm that he does not extend during the rebound.
Kurucs (BKN) slightly turns his body as he absorbs the contact from Connaughton (MIL) after the release of his intended pass.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Johnson's (BKN) hip at the start of the drive, but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Mason (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Johnson (BKN) and Williiams (MIL) cleanly blocks the shot.
At the start of the drive, Johnson (BKN) moves into Ilyasova's (MIL) space and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
Williams (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Johnson's (BKN) path and firms up to absorb the contact.
Temple (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position and makes clean hand on ball contact during the driving shot attempt by Mason (MIL).  A jump ball is correctly called.
Prior to any contact with Kurucs (BKN), Williams (MIL) enters the semi-circle prematurely and a jump ball violation is correctly called.
Kurucs (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in DiVincenzo's (MIL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.  He places a hand on him as he disengages, but the contact is marginal.
Connaughton (MIL) makes incidental contact to Johnson's (BKN) arm after the release that does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally on his shot at the basket.
During the drive, Chiozza (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on Mason (MIL) and any contact is incidental.  He does not cause Mason to lose control of the ball.
Kurucs (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on Mason (MIL) and cleanly gathers the loose ball.
Kurucs (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in Mason's (MIL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
DiVincenzo (MIL) gathers on his right foot and takes two legal steps on his drive to the basket.
During the switch on the pick, Kurucs (BKN) and DiVincenzo (MIL) engage and separate during the cut to the basket.
Temple (BKN) briefly grasps Korver's jersey and releases it during the inbound.
DiVincenzo (MIL) makes marginal contact to Chiozza (BKN) as he attempts to disengage and cut to the ball.
Temple (BKN) and Williams (MIL) engage and disengage off-ball.
Martin (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on DiVincenzo (MIL) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
